      "content": {
        "title": "ACL Imaging and Associated Injury",
        "definition": "MRI tear pattern, bone bruise, Segond fracture, and meniscal status.",
        "summary": "Lateral meniscus more often injured acutely; medial in chronic ACL deficiency."
